  "textPreview": "Free June 9 event: How to win brand visibility when AI decides what gets seen →\nSolutions\nTools\nResources\nPricing\nEN\nSign in\nRequest a demo\nStart free trial\nSERP Tracker\n\nSE Ranking's SERP checker simplifies and streamlines the process of obtaining SERP data for any keyword. One click is all it takes to gain insights into the strengths and weaknesses of top-ranking pages.\n\nStart free trial\nCheck SERP for free\nBuild a smart SEO strategy with the SERP checker tool\n\nSERP checker is a state of the art tool for examining your competitors’ site performance in search and getting an insider’s look at their SEO strategy. Use it it to delve deeper into the metrics that help your competitors maintain top positions on the SERPs, including text length, content structure, page load speed, and keyword usage & distribution throughout the content.\n\nContent and on-page analysis\nGain valuable insights into keyword density, word count, and readability metrics. Enhance your meta title and description to improve CTR and secure top positions on SERPs.\nPage experience\nAnalyze core web vitals and optimize interactivity for enhanced user engagement. Improve loading speed, visual stability, and the text/HTML ratio to deliver a seamless browsing experience.\nDomain metrics\nDiscover your competitors' domain authority to set powerful SEO strategies. Easily access crucial domain metrics, such as domain age, domain trust score, referring domains count, and even forecasted traffic.\nSERP Analyzer\n\nCheck the SERP for key SEO metrics to identify shared commonalities among your competitors. Tailor this analysis according to your preferences by selecting the specific metrics you wish to evaluate.\n\nCreate brand-new pages based on what works for your organic competitors\n\nExclude websites that you aren’t competing against\n\nCheck up to the top 50 organic results\n\nGet insights on traffic, keywords, and backlinks\n\nAnalyze SERP for 110+ on-page and off-page metrics\n\nLearn the on-page quality score of each top p",
